  "keyFeatures": [
    "OpenAI-compatible API (chat completions, embeddings, responses, batches)",
    "Pluggable provider architecture supporting 20+ inference backends",
    "Server-side agentic orchestration with tool calling and MCP integration",
    "Built-in RAG with vector stores and file search",
    "Safety guardrails via Llama Guard and other safety providers",
    "Evaluation framework for measuring model and application quality",
    "Telemetry and observability built-in",
    "Kubernetes and cloud deployment support",
    "Distribution system for pre-configured deployments (starter, NVIDIA, Dell, etc.)",
    "Recording/replay test infrastructure for deterministic CI"
  ],
